---
title: Rainbow Pesto Pasta (V) with roasted tomato, squash and walnut pesto
description: Packed with fresh and vibrant vegetables combined with a walnut pesto this dish is a veggie winner. Pesto originates from the city of Genoa and this Italian inspiration is the flavour that underpins this tasty treasure. Make sure you finish it with a sprinkling of hard Italian cheese this will compliment the nutty pesto and top off a great tasting dish.
